-- EU Commission Plans 9 Billion-Euro Budget Increase, Welt Reports
-- B y   J a n a   R a n d o w
-- 2012-04-23T07:04:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-23/eu-commission-plans-9-billion-euro-budget-increase-welt-reports.html
The European Commission plans to
boost the European Union’s budget by about 9 billion euros ($12
billion) next year,  Germany ’s  Die Welt  newspaper reported.  That’s an increase of 6 percent compared with the 2012
budget, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Randow in Frankfurt at 
